cs.CV, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper deals with visual sensor networks and distributed algorithms for feature extraction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses network communication and coordination, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper proposes a distributed algorithm, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper mentions real-time visual analysis, which could also relate to cs.MM (Multimedia).
